(c) register a Strata Management Statement and By-Law. Under the Current Law, Lot Entitlements are required to be specified in the Strata Plan. Under the Amendment Law, Lot Entitlements will also need to be specified in the Strata Management Statement (as well as in the Strata Plan), with Services Charges to take into account the beneficial use of the Common Property.   
